{"tid":457623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國未開打,金仔先腳軟喊：「說好的人權呢？」","createTime":"2017-11-04T05:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T05:44:40.000Z","uid":31637,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b4bb675e86b8cce6e43b4c3a1ff12fc7635daae6","tid":457623,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T05:17:03.000Z","msg":"北韓周五呼籲停止針對該國的「殘酷制裁」，形容西方在北韓最新核試後實施的制裁措施，相當於「種族滅絕」。<br />\n<br />\n北韓駐日內瓦聯合國的代表團發表聲明說，美國今日牽頭對北韓施加的殘酷制裁和壓力，是當代違反人權的暴行，尤如種族滅絕。聲明又說，有關制裁「威脅和損害北韓人民各方面的人權」。<br />\n北韓要求立刻停止制裁之際，美國總統特朗普正出訪亞洲，尋求各國協助迫使北韓放棄製造核危機。<br />\n美國上月單方面向7名北韓人和3間北韓公司實施制裁，指他們涉及嚴重違反人權，包括強迫勞動。在9月，聯合國安理會亦加強對北韓制裁，包括出口禁令及凍結多名北韓官員資產及實施旅遊限制。<br />\n聯合國一名專家上月曾表示，國際制裁將損害北韓的主要經濟環節，令平壤人民的人權受損。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171104/57415905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171104%2F57415905&d=CBPArazkphjuhTk%2BmDAdN6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=a3efcaa6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171104%2F57415905&h=37b6fc6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171104/57415905</a><br />\n<br />\n我發現Ｄ獨裁國家真係好撚好野，佢地玩流氓手段就得，人地玩流氓手段以牙還牙就唔得，古有中國人喊說好的民主呢，今有北韓人喊說好的人權呢，型既盡頭便是柒，金仔今次真係柒撚到上太空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb65b24fead660464542ac723ef83e38fde3d84c","tid":457623,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T05:18:03.000Z","msg":"吹啦 , 繼續吹啦"},{"pid":"55b5131b96a6cbc747363089d30b47aeb5a75a9e","tid":457623,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T05:19:28.000Z","msg":"又要威又要西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc210091e4a2b60b767a78311dc4bd993acf0e1","tid":457623,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T05:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8898e49d7fa121d33f73172bf3761a4910df45d","tid":457623,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T05:23:03.000Z","msg":"之前係支那一路唔遵守un禁運運野比北泡"},{"pid":"24c9dca7c9b12866eee9aca0990c89d2f4e961a6","tid":457623,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T05:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁唔滿意你咪射2支飛彈 等人有籍口打柒你 大家唔洗煩"},{"pid":"e100b830e1e868d942be3d39dd77297f0eba71d4","tid":457623,"uid":106247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T05:44:40.000Z","msg":"凍結多名北韓官員資產<br />\n上面先係重點，其他金仔wfc"}]}